       &kp RIGHT_BRACKET      &kp LS(EQUAL)     &kp NUHS                       &kp RA(EQUAL)     &none               &kp RA(N7)  &kp LS(N8)        &kp EQUAL            &kp LS(N9)  &kp RA(N0)
&none  &kp RA(RIGHT_BRACKET)  &kp SLASH         &kp LS(RBKT)                   &kp MINUS         &none               &kp NUBS    &kp RA(N8)        &kp LS(NON_US_HASH)  &kp RA(N9)  &kp LS(NON_US_BACKSLASH)  &none
                                                &trans                         &mo 3             &trans              &trans      &trans            &trans
